{
  "$description": "Dark-theme overrides — ONLY the semantic color layer is repointed at different primitives; primitives, radius, typography and motion are NOT duplicated. Emitted into the `.dark` block of tokens.css. Reproduces the current `.dark` palette 1:1.",
